{"word":"ἀφικνέομαι","slug":"ἀφικνέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀφιϰνέομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a>, ἱϰνέομαι</el> ‘come to’] ‘arrive at a certain point’, but not in sense of coming to a physical space as in older usage, <b><i>reach</i></b> = <i>become known to</i> <b><a href='B:520 16:19'>Ro 16:19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀφίημι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀφιλάγαθος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}